<div class="app-path-container"><%= link_to "Home ", articles_path%>/Help</div>
<div class="bounding-container">
    <div class="help-container">
        <div class="help-faq-title">FAQs</div>
        <div class="help-questions">
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">How do I sign up?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can sign up by clicking on the green "SIGN UP" button in 
                                        the upper right corner of you browser window, where all articles are posted.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">How do I log in?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can log in by clicking on the "Log In" button in the navigation 
                                        bar at the top of your browser window.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Is having an account and posting articles for free?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">Registering to our website will always be free and users will never 
                                        be charged for creating any content.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Can I write an article?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">Once you are logged in to your profile you can create an article 
                                        by clicking on "Write" button from the navigation menu at the top 
                                        of your browser window.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Can I post an article?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can post an article by clicking on "Publish" button below 
                                        write/edit article page.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Can I edit my article?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can edit your article by clicking on "Edit" button which 
                                        will appear when hovering over the three dots icon to the right 
                                        of the article.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Can I delete my article?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can delete your article by clicking on "Delete" button which 
                                        will appear when hovering over the three dots icon to the right 
                                        of the article.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Can I view article comments?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can view all article comments by clicking on the comment icon 
                                        located below article.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Can I post a comment?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can post a comment by clicking on the "Post" button in 
                                        below text input area.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Can I edit my comment?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can edit your comment by clicking on "Edit" button which 
                                        will appear when hovering over the three dots icon to the right 
                                        of each comment.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Can I delete a comment?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can delete a comment by clicking on "Delete" button which 
                                        will appear when hovering over the three dots icon to the right 
                                        of each comment.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Can I delete all my articles?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can delete all your articles by clicking on the "Delete All Articles" 
                                        button in the settings page which can be found hovering on your initial 
                                        in the upper right corner of your browser window.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Can I delete all my comments?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can delete all your comments by clicking on the "Delete All Comments" 
                                        button in the settings page which can be found hovering on your initial 
                                        in the upper right corner of your browser window.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="help-question">
                <div class="help-question-title">Can I delete my account?</div>
                <div class="help-answer">You can delete your account by clicking on the "Delete User Profile" 
                                        button in the settings page which can be found hovering on your initial 
                                        in the upper right corner of your browser window.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>